    <div class="">
        
<p>My favorite music comes from the source itself sole aka&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sole_(hip_hop_artist)" target="_self">tim holland</a>. You should buy his music, his life depends upon it.</p><p>site:&nbsp;<a href="https://soleone.org/" target="_self">https://soleone.org</a></p><p>buy:&nbsp;<a href="https://music.apple.com/us/artist/sole/1038548378" target="_self">apple music</a>, djpain1 on <a href="https://music.apple.com/us/artist/dj-pain-1/253213713" target="_self">apple music</a></p><p>listen:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.patreon.com/soleone" target="_self">patreon</a></p><p>free:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCNgr48RvKC9uz6JLdNEO48w" target="_self">Youtube</a>&nbsp;(<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@soleonedotorg/videos" target="_self">Archives</a>)</p>    </div>

